  ('Xano', 'xano', 'Headless backend for APIs and databases; modular for complex apps.', 'Headless backend for APIs and databases; modular for complex apps. Best for: modular for complex logic-heavy apps/SaaS backends.. Pricing: Free tier; Launch $99/mo.', 'Website Creation', 'freemium', 'high', 4.5, 'https://xano.com', false),
