  ('Saatosa', 'saatosa', 'AI/Web3 templates for SaaS sites; zero-code complex UIs.', 'AI/Web3 templates for SaaS sites; zero-code complex UIs. Best for: zero-code complex UIs/dApps.. Pricing: Not specified alphadesignpro.substack.', 'Website Creation', 'unknown', 'medium', 4.5, 'https://saatosa.com', false),
